ission. Due to our enhanced\nangular resolution of $<1\\,\\mathrm{arcsec}$, we find further streaming motion\nwithin the inner arcsecond, that have not been detected until now. Despite the\nflow of gas towards the centre, no signs for significant AGN activity are\nfound. This raises the questions what determines whether the infalling gas will\nfuel an AGN or star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 16:29:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
