 reveal that the cutoff positions depend on not only\nthe intensity and wavelength of the pulse, but also its duration, in marked\ncontrast to the gas-phase case. Our model can be viewed as a solid-state and\nmomentum-space counterpart of the familiar three-step model, highly successful\nfor gas-phase HHG, and provide a unified basis to understand HHG from\nsolid-state materials and gaseous media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 23:39:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 07:39:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2017 08:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
